msgid "Return to Heart of the Elders, Part 1"
msgstr "重返久远腹地，第一章"

msgid "Scenario V–A: Return to Heart of the Elders, Part 1"
msgstr "冒险V–A：重返久远腹地，第一章"

msgid "Remove the Act 1a—\"Search for the Pattern\" from the game and replace it with the new Act 1a—\"A Familiar Pattern.\""
msgstr "将场景1a——“研究图案”从游戏中移除，用新版的场景la——“熟悉的图案”替换。"

msgid "Create the exploration deck. Gather all of the single-sided [[Jungle]] locations. Include only 1 of the 2 locations with each of the following connection symbols, chosen at random."
msgstr "构建探索牌堆。拿取所有单面的[[丛林]]地点，对于以下每个连接符号的地点，只随机加入2个地点中的1个。"

msgid "Remove the other 4 [[Jungle]] locations from the game. Do not include any of the other encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions."
msgstr "将其他4个[[丛林]]地点从游戏中移除，不要查看。不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。(卡牌总数应为6张。)"

msgid "For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rules apply:"
msgstr "在本场冒险期间，增加以下额外规则："

msgid "The 'check your supplies' ability on the Mouth of K'n-yan can be used from any location."
msgstr "昆扬之口的‘查看你的补给品’能力可以在任意地点使用。"

msgid "<b>Forced</b> - After a successful exploration ends: Shuffle the top card of the encounter deck into the exploration deck."
msgstr "<b>强制</b> - 在一次成功探索结束后：将遭遇牌堆顶的1张卡牌混洗入探索牌堆。"

msgid "The puzzle has not been solved, you can either try again or choose to proceed anyway. The investigators must decide (choose one):"
msgstr "谜题尚未解开，你可以选择再次尝试，或者不顾一切推进。调查员必须选择(以下一项)："

msgid "Continue to try by replaying <b>Scenario V-A: Heart of the Elders, Part 1</b>."
msgstr "再次尝试，重玩<b>冒险V–A：久远腹地，第一章</b>。"

msgid "Proceed to <b>Resolution 2</b>"
msgstr "进入<b>结局2</b>"

msgid "<i>You have a bad feeling about this…</i>"
msgstr "<i>你有一种不好的预感……</i>"

msgid "The investigators must replay <b>Scenario V-A: Return to Heart of the Elders, Part 1</b>. Reset the game to this scenario’s <b>Setup</b>. Do not record anything else in your Campaign Log except for any trauma suffered from your previous game. No experience points are earned from your previous game. Any player whose investigator was killed or driven insane must choose a new investigator to play, as normal."
msgstr "调查员必须重玩<b>冒险V–A：重返久远腹地，第一章</b>。重置游戏至本场冒险的<b>设置阶段</b>。除了在上一局游戏中受到的任何创伤以外，不要在冒险日志记录其他任何信息。你们在上一局游戏不获得经验点数。任何玩家的调查员如已阵亡或发疯，则他必须如常选择一位新的调查员入场。"

msgid "You have trespassed in a hostile land. Place pillar tokens on the Mouth of K'n-yan until there are exactly 6 pillar tokens. For every pillar token added in this way, record two tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\" in your Campaign Log."
msgstr "你擅自闯入了危险禁地。在昆扬之口上放置石柱标记，直到正好有6个石柱标记。然后，每以此方式放置1个石柱标记，在你冒险日志的“伊格之怒”下方作2次记录。"

msgid "Record 12 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作12次记录。"

msgid "Record 10 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作10次记录。"

msgid "Record 8 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作8次记录。"

msgid "Record 6 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作6次记录。"

msgid "Record 4 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作4次记录。"

msgid "Record 2 tally marks under \"Yig's Fury\"."
msgstr "在“伊格之怒”下方作2次记录。"

msgid "As you pass the pillars, intense pain wrenches its way through your body, and you are afflicted with a terrible curse. Each investigator who is poisoned takes 1 mental trauma. Each investigator who is not poisoned adds a set-aside Poisoned weakness to their deck."
msgstr "你经过石柱时，钻心的疼痛传遍你的全身，你被施加了可怕的诅咒。每位中毒的调查员受到1点精神创伤。每位未中毒的调查员将一张放在一边的中毒弱点卡加入自己的牌组。"

msgid "You haven't yet completed the puzzle of the six pillars that serve as the entrance to K'n-yan, but you don't wish to tarry any further in this hostile jungle. You decide to enter the cavern anyway, hoping that whatever \"wards\" the pillars represent are nothing but ancient superstition…"
msgstr "你并没有完成昆扬入口处六根石柱的谜题，但你也不想在这片危险丛林中多逗留了。你决定就这么直接进入洞穴，希望这些石柱所代表的“结界”只不过是古人的迷信而已……"
